  "title": "Preschool English Teacher",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Plan and implement age-appropriate learning activities that cater to the cognitive, emotional, social, and physical development of young children (typically aged 2-6 years).</li>\n  <li>Observe, assess, and document children's progress and learning outcomes to ensure they meet developmental milestones.</li>\n  <li>Create a safe and nurturing environment that promotes positive learning experiences and fosters children's curiosity, creativity, and independence.</li>\n  <li>Ensure the safety and well-being of all children in the care of the educator, including compliance with health and safety protocols (e.g., proper hygiene, first aid).</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Early Childhood Care and Education (DECCE) or equivalent, recognized by the Early Childhood Development Agency (ECDA).</li>\n</ul>",
