    "description": "<p>MapleBear Tai Seng is located above Tai Seng MRT. &nbsp;MapleBear caters to children from 18 months onwards.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our program adapts according to the needs of our children.&nbsp;We at MapleBear have a low teacher-to-child ratio to ensure that every child receives proper attention and guidance as we aspire them to be a competent global citizen in the future. With our strong bilingual programme anchored from the Canadian early childhood curriculum, our children learn both English &amp; Mandarin through enriching activities that are exciting and meaningful to them. Our curriculum aims to develop curious, creative, confident students who communicate well and able to collaborate for greater success. As a premium early years education provider, we offer a conducive learning environment that includes an indoor playground, a music room, and interactive classrooms.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We believe that through collaboration with parents, we are able to provide the best education and life skills that our future generation rightfully deserve.</p>",
